{"pageTitle":"kafka 소개 - kafka 연습","title":"kafka 소개","content":"<h3 id=\"98gtn\" name=\"%E5%88%9D%E8%AF%86-Kafka\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 16px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; font-weight: bold;\">初识 Kafka</strong></h3><h4 id=\"echj5\" name=\"%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF-Kafka\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 12px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; font-weight: bold;\">什么是 Kafka</strong></h4><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Kafka 是由 <code style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(243, 245, 249); border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; color: rgb(10, 191, 91); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, monospace; line-height: 20px;\">Linkedin</code> 公司开发的，它是一个分布式的，支持多分区、多副本，基于 Zookeeper 的分布式消息流平台，它同时也是一款开源的<strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; font-weight: bold;\">基于发布订阅模式的消息引擎系统</strong>。</p><h4 id=\"4b3ja\" name=\"Kafka-%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%AF%E8%AF%AD\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 16px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; font-weight: bold;\">Kafka 的基本术语</strong></h4><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">消息：Kafka 中的数据单元被称为<code style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(243, 245, 249); border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; color: rgb(10, 191, 91); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, monospace; line-height: 20px;\">消息</code>，也被称为记录，可以把它看作<span class=\"mod-overview__keyword\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 4px; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(0, 82, 217); padding-right: 10px; background-image: url(&quot;images/icon-keyword_32a.svg&quot;); background-position: right 2px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: 8px 8px; box-shadow: none; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all;\">数据库</span>表中某一行的记录。</p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">批次：为了提高效率， 消息会<code style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(243, 245, 249); border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; color: rgb(10, 191, 91); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, monospace; line-height: 20px;\">分批次</code>写入 Kafka，批次就代指的是一组消息。</p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">主题：消息的种类称为 <code style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(243, 245, 249); border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; color: rgb(10, 191, 91); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, monospace; line-height: 20px;\">主题</code>（Topic）,可以说一个主题代表了一类消息。相当于是对消息进行分类。主题就像是数据库中的表。</p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">分区：主题可以被分为若干个分区（partition），同一个主题中的分区可以不在一个机器上，有可能会部署在多个机器上，由此来实现 kafka 的<code style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(243, 245, 249); border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; color: rgb(10, 191, 91); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, monospace; line-height: 20px;\">伸缩性</code>，单一主题中的分区有序，但是无法保证主题中所有的分区有序</p><figure class=\"\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; margin: 16px 0px; display: block; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><div class=\"rno-markdown-img-url\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; list-style: inherit;\"><div class=\"rno-markdown-img-url-inner\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: inline-block; white-space: normal !important; list-style: inherit; width: 996px;\"><div style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; width: 996px;\"><img src=\"https://ask.qcloudimg.com/http-save/5418473/pyuuucobqb.png?imageView2/2/w/660\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; cursor: zoom-in; width: 996px; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; border-radius: 3px;\"></div></div></div></figure><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">生产者：向主题发布消息的客户端应用程序称为<code style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(243, 245, 249); border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; color: rgb(10, 191, 91); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, monospace; line-height: 20px;\">生产者</code>（Producer），生产者用于持续不断的向某个主题发送消息。</p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">消费者：订阅主题消息的客户端程序称为<code style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(243, 245, 249); border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; color: rgb(10, 191, 91); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, monospace; line-height: 20px;\">消费者</code>（Consumer），消费者用于处理生产者产生的消息。</p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">消费者群组：生产者与消费者的关系就如同餐厅中的厨师和顾客之间的关系一样，一个厨师对应多个顾客，也就是一个生产者对应多个消费者，<code style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(243, 245, 249); border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; color: rgb(10, 191, 91); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, monospace; line-height: 20px;\">消费者群组</code>（Consumer Group）指的就是由一个或多个消费者组成的群体。</p><figure class=\"\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; margin: 16px 0px; display: block; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><div class=\"rno-markdown-img-url\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; list-style: inherit;\"><div class=\"rno-markdown-img-url-inner\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: inline-block; white-space: normal !important; list-style: inherit; width: 996px;\"><div style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; width: 996px;\"><img src=\"https://ask.qcloudimg.com/http-save/5418473/tg4jlig3il.jpeg?imageView2/2/w/660\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; cursor: zoom-in; width: 996px; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; border-radius: 3px;\"></div></div></div></figure><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">偏移量：<code style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(243, 245, 249); border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; color: rgb(10, 191, 91); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, monospace; line-height: 20px;\">偏移量</code>（Consumer Offset）是一种元数据，它是一个不断递增的整数值，用来记录消费者发生重平衡时的位置，以便用来恢复数据。</p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">broker: 一个独立的 Kafka <span class=\"mod-overview__keyword\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 4px; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(0, 82, 217); padding-right: 10px; background-image: url(&quot;images/icon-keyword_32a.svg&quot;); background-position: right 2px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: 8px 8px; box-shadow: none; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all;\">服务器</span>就被称为 <code style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(243, 245, 249); border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; color: rgb(10, 191, 91); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, monospace; line-height: 20px;\">broker</code>，broker 接收来自生产者的消息，为消息设置偏移量，并提交消息到磁盘保存。</p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">broker 集群：broker 是<code style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(243, 245, 249); border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; color: rgb(10, 191, 91); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, monospace; line-height: 20px;\">集群</code> 的组成部分，broker 集群由一个或多个 broker 组成，每个集群都有一个 broker 同时充当了<code style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(243, 245, 249); border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; color: rgb(10, 191, 91); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, monospace; line-height: 20px;\">集群控制器</code>的角色（自动从集群的活跃成员中选举出来）。</p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">副本：Kafka 中消息的备份又叫做 <code style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; background-color: rgb(243, 245, 249); border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; color: rgb(10, 191, 91); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, monospace; line-height: 20px;\">副本</code>（Replica），副本的数量是可以配置的，Kafka 定义了两类副本：领导者副本（Leader Replica） 和 追随者副本（Follower Replica），前者对外提供服务，后者只是被动跟随。</p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: inherit; min-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;pingfang SC&quot;, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei ui&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">重平衡：Rebalance。消费者组内某个消费者实例挂掉后，其他消费者实例自动重新分配订阅主题分区的过程。Rebalance 是 Kafka 消费者端实现高可用的重要手段。</p>"}